    "body": "On CPU, using MoE models will fail because`fp8_utils` imports `triton`\n\n```bash\nvllm serve deepseek-ai/DeepSeek-V2-Lite-Chat --trust-remote-code\n```\n\n```\nERROR 04-01 08:52:04 [registry.py:332]   File \"/home/thien/code/vllm_cpu/vllm/model_executor/models/deepseek_v2.py\", line 38, in <module>\nERROR 04-01 08:52:04 [registry.py:332]     from vllm.model_executor.layers.fused_moe import FusedMoE\nERROR 04-01 08:52:04 [registry.py:332]   File \"/home/thien/code/vllm_cpu/vllm/model_executor/layers/fused_moe/__init__.py\", line 6, in <module>\nERROR 04-01 08:52:04 [registry.py:332]     from vllm.model_executor.layers.fused_moe.layer import (\nERROR 04-01 08:52:04 [registry.py:332]   File \"/home/thien/code/vllm_cpu/vllm/model_executor/layers/fused_moe/layer.py\", line 19, in <module>\nERROR 04-01 08:52:04 [registry.py:332]     from vllm.model_executor.layers.fused_moe.rocm_aiter_fused_moe import (\nERROR 04-01 08:52:04 [registry.py:332]   File \"/home/thien/code/vllm_cpu/vllm/model_executor/layers/fused_moe/rocm_aiter_fused_moe.py\", line 7, in <module>\nERROR 04-01 08:52:04 [registry.py:332]     from vllm.model_executor.layers.quantization.utils.fp8_utils import (\nERROR 04-01 08:52:04 [registry.py:332]   File \"/home/thien/code/vllm_cpu/vllm/model_executor/layers/quantization/utils/fp8_utils.py\", line 10, in <module>\nERROR 04-01 08:52:04 [registry.py:332]     import triton\nERROR 04-01 08:52:04 [registry.py:332] ModuleNotFoundError: No module named 'triton'\n```\n\nThis PR moves `fp8_utils` import to the function requires it to avoid global `triton` import.",
    "created_at": "2025-04-01T00:54:13Z",
    "updated_at": "2025-04-02T03:35:22Z",
    "closed_at": "2025-04-02T03:33:55Z",
